## Endpoint de verificación

```csharp
app.MapGet("/inventory/verify",
async (LibraryDbContext db) =>
{
    var negative =
        await db.Inventory.AnyAsync(
            i => i.CurrentStock < 0);

    var totalUsed =
        await db.Inventory.SumAsync(
            i => i.InitialStock -
                 i.CurrentStock);

    var fulfilled =
        await db.Orders
            .Where(o =>
                o.Status ==
                Status.Fulfilled)
            .SelectMany(o => o.Lines)
            .SumAsync(l => l.Quantity);

    return new
    {
        NegativeStock = negative,

        TotalUsed = totalUsed,

        TotalFulfilled = fulfilled,

        AllTerminal =
            await db.Orders.AllAsync(
                o => o.Status !=
                Status.Pending)
    };
});
```

